components.mapscreen

Class MapScreen

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.layout.Region
          • javafx.scene.layout.Pane
            • javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane
              • components.mapscreen.MapScreen
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class MapScreen
extends javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane
    This class wraps the canvas and the tooltips and show the dynamic view of the cityMap (intersection when click on it, delivery address when click on it, warehouse when click on it)
